wikipedia_page.main: William Andrew (22 March 1869 – 30 March 1911) was an English first-class cricketer who played his games for  Hampshire County Cricket Club.    His highest score of 106 came when playing for Hampshire in the match against Warwickshire County Cricket Club.   His best bowling of 5/157 came when playing for Hampshire in the match against Sussex County Cricket Club.He also played 3 Minor Counties Championship games for Dorset.
